<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL4">
<l>moyttaval viṉaiyuḷ niṉṟu mūṉṟeḻut tuṭaiya pērāṟ</l>
<l>kattira pantu maṉṟē parāṅkati kaṇṭu koṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>ittaṉai yaṭiya rāṉārk kiraṅkunam maraṅka ṉāya</l>
<l>pittaṉaip peṟṟu mantō piṟaviyuṭ piṇaṅku māṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even Kṣatrabandhu came to see for himself the highest state—did he not? —</l>
<l>[even while] remaining among the strong karman that swarmed around [him]</l>
<l>thanks to the three-syllabled name!</l>
<l>Alas! How does one get entangled in births,</l>
<l>despite possessing the Madman who is our Lord of Raṅgam</l>
<l>who shows such compassion for [His] servants!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
